      "role": "user",
      "content": "Today I learned the word \"perspective.\" I saw it in a movie review. But I am not sure how to use it properly. Can you give me an example? Also, I watched a football match yesterday—super exciting! It was Real Madrid vs. Barcelona. Did you follow that?"
    },
    {
