      "content": "Real Madrid won 2-0. It was a great game—Cristiano Ronaldo scored both goals! I am so happy for him. I also learned the word \"strategy\" today. It was in a movie about a bank heist. I think I know how to use it. Can I try? For example: \"The police used a good strategy to catch the thieves.\" Is this correct?"
    },
    {
