      "content": "I watched \"Mission Impossible: Fallout\"—very exciting! Tom Cruise does all the stunts himself—unbelievable! I heard the word \"precise\" in that movie. I think it means very exact. Am I right? And I feel more confident every day, thanks to you! Aapki help bahut accha hai."
